# ============================================================================
# LargeFileBridge .gitignore
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This file IS the bridge. Its whole job is to keep large binary files OUT of
# Git history so pushes stay small and never hit GitHub's 100 MB limit.
#
# The files ignored below are NOT lost — they are synced between your computers
# out-of-band over IPFS or peer-to-peer sync (Syncthing-style). Git tracks the
# code + a manifest of what should exist; the p2p layer moves the actual bytes.
#
# Rule of thumb: if it's big and binary, ignore it here and let the bridge sync
# it. If it's small and text, let Git track it.
# ============================================================================

# --- The dedicated large-file drop zone (synced via p2p, never committed) ---
large/
Large/
LargeFiles/

# --- Video ------------------------------------------------------------------
*.mp4
*.mov
*.mkv
*.avi
*.wmv
*.flv
*.webm
*.m4v
*.mpg
*.mpeg
*.prores

# --- Audio ------------------------------------------------------------------
*.wav
*.aiff
*.aif
*.flac
*.m4a
*.mp3
*.ogg

# --- Images (large / source formats) ----------------------------------------
*.psd
*.psb
*.ai
*.tif
*.tiff
*.raw
*.cr2
*.nef
*.arw
*.dng
*.exr
*.hdr

# --- 3D / render / DCC assets -----------------------------------------------
*.blend
*.blend1
*.fbx
*.obj
*.abc
*.usd
*.usdz
*.glb
*.gltf
*.ply

# --- AI / ML model weights & data -------------------------------------------
*.ckpt
*.safetensors
*.pt
*.pth
*.bin
*.onnx
*.gguf
*.npz
*.h5

# --- Archives & disk images -------------------------------------------------
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.gz
*.7z
*.rar
*.dmg
*.iso

# --- Datasets ---------------------------------------------------------------
*.csv.gz
*.parquet
*.sqlite
*.db

# --- OS / editor cruft ------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NOTE: The manifest that records the ignored large files (paths + IPFS CIDs /
# content hashes) is INTENTIONALLY tracked by Git. Do not add it here.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
